programme.desc: Fast-paced with music, ISO angles, and commentary, Netbusters offers an alternative review of every goal and key moment from the latest round of Premier League fixtures.

programme.title: Ep37: Andoni Iraola : PL Stories
programme.desc: Andoni Iraola went from relative obscurity to leading a once relegation-threatened club to its highest ever points tally in the Premier League. We explore how his fearless philosophy, tactical innovation and emotional connection to the game have driven his teams to challenge expectations and rewrite their identity. A story of a Basque footballing icon, and his remarkable journey from Cyprus to the Premier League with Bournemouth in 5 years.

programme.title: Fri 13 Feb : Review
programme.desc: Review brings you all the action from Matchweek 26, featuring the midweek fixtures with Leeds trip to Chelsea, West Ham host Manchester United, and Thursday's fixture as Arsenal take on Brentford in West London.

programme.title: Thu 12 Feb : The Midweek Wrap
programme.desc: The Midweek Wrap features comprehensive match highlights, the best post-match reaction and expert analysis from a high-class team of pundits.

programme.title: Ep25: Petr Cech : The Big Interview
programme.desc: In a career spanning 20 years, Petr Cech established himself as one of the greatest goalkeepers the game has ever seen. This week, The Big Interview sits down with the four-time Premier League champion to reflect on his playing career and the mentality it takes to be a goalkeeper at the very pinnacle of world football. Cech reflects on his journey from Plzen to becoming the only player record 200 clean sheets in the Premier League. Cech talks us through the challenges he had to overcome, the unique mental attitude needed to thrive between the goalposts, and his transition into ice hockey after his football career.

programme.title: Ep07: Jimmy Floyd Hasselbaink : PL Moments
programme.desc: Over a nine season spell in the Premier League, Jimmy Floyd Hasselbaink etched his name into footballing folklore as one of the most dynamic goalscorers in the competition's history. Fourth all time in Premier League goals for Chelsea, Hasselbaink's iconic freekicks and powerful finishes have seen him score some of the League's most memorable goals. This week, the Dutch international sits down with PL Moments to break down how to strike the ball, and talk us through his ten favourite moments from his Premier League career.

programme.title: Ep15: Edwin van Der Sar : PL Stories
programme.desc: Edwin van der Sar has faced down pressure on the biggest stages in world football, but his toughest battle came after retirement. In 2023, the legendary goalkeeper suffered a life-threatening brain haemorrhage. In this episode Edwin opens up on his recovery and looks back on his career at the top that redefined goalkeeping. From Champions League glory with Ajax and Manchester United to his commanding presence in the Premier League, Van der Sar was the calm at the heart of some of football's greatest teams. We also explore his post-playing career as a respected executive, his role in Ajax's modern renaissance, and how his recent health scare has reshaped his outlook on life.

programme.title: Ep30: The Forgotten Class Of 92 : PL Stories
programme.desc: Three decades on from Manchester United's iconic Class of '92, PL Stories steps beyond the headline names to rediscover the teammates who shared the same dressing room, dreams, and demands of one of football's most revered youth systems. We sit down with the lesser-known graduates who lived that journey first-hand, players whose paths diverged from the global spotlight but whose experiences offer a rare and revealing window into the reality behind the legend. Through candid interviews and unseen archive moments, they reflect on the pressure of following in the footsteps of club greats, the bonds forged on the training pitches of The Cliff, and the pivotal moments that shaped the rest of their lives.

programme.title: Ep27: (Subbed) Gary Neville: Premier League Hall Of Fame : PL Stories
programme.desc: We sit down for an exclusive interview with the second of two new Premier League Hall of fame inductees, Gary Neville. From his journey from Class of '92 prodigy to Premier League Hall of Fame icon, he talks us through the moments that defined his legacy at Manchester United. A story on one of the league's most influential right-backs and a leader whose impact still shapes English football today.

programme.title: Ep26: (Subbed) Eden Hazard: Premier League Hall Of Fame : PL Stories
programme.desc: We sit down for an exclusive interview with the first of two new Premier League Hall of fame inductees, Eden Hazard. A celebrated footballer who lit up the English top-flight during his illustrious career; a winner of multiple domestic and European honours, he became a true legend of the Premier League era. He reflects on his rise to the top, the moments that defined his career, and the immense pride he feels at joining the elite ranks of the Premier League's greatest ever players.

programme.title: Ep03: (Subbed) PL Goalscorers : PL Stories
programme.desc: We celebrate the greatest goalscorers in Premier League history; the icons whose instinct, power, and flair have lit up stadiums and etched their names into footballing folklore. From Alan Shearer's relentless consistency to Thierry Henry's elegance, Sergio Aguero's killer instinct to Harry Kane's rise, we relive the moments that defined an era.

programme.title: Ep32: (Subbed) Micky van De ven : PL Stories
programme.desc: We reflect on the rapid rise of Micky van de Ven, tracing his journey from a promising young defender in the Netherlands to becoming one of the Premier League's most electrifying modern centrebacks. We sit down with van de Ven to explore the resilience, mentality and sheer speed, on and off the pitch that have defined his ascent. Travelling back to the places and people that shaped him, we uncover the grounding influences, bold decisions and breakthrough moments that propelled him to the top of the game.

programme.title: Tot v Ars : Classic Match

programme.title: Ep02: Sol Campbell : PL Moments
programme.desc: Premier League Moments sits down with one of the most dominant centre-backs the league has ever seen. Sol Campbell rose through the ranks at Tottenham Hotspur before making one of the most controversial moves in Premier League history, when he crossed the divide to join rivals Arsenal. programme.desc: Dahulu Kala, Terdapat Sebuah Planet Bernama Machina Dimana Metal Cardbots Tinggal. Suatu Ketika, Planet Ini Tiba-Tiba Meledak Dan Memaksa Semua Penghuninya Untuk Hidup Di Bumi. Agar Tidak Menarik Perhatian Makhluk Bumi, Cardbots Menyamar Sebagai Kendaraan Sehari-Hari. Hingga Suatu Hari, Seorang Anak Sekolah Dasar Yang Bernama Jun Secara Tidak Sengaja Menemukan Metal Breath, Dengan Metal Breath Tersebut Dia Bisa Menangkap Dan Menyalakan Cardbots Dengan Kemampuan Yang Berbeda.

programme.title: Beyblade X
programme.desc: Beyblade X Mengikuti Kisah Robin Kazami, Seorang Blader Muda Yang Ditinggalkan Timnya Setelah Kekalahan Telak. Dia Kemudian Bertemu Dengan Jaxon Cross, Mantan Juara Beyblade, Dan Mereka Berdua Membentuk Tim Baru Bernama Tim Persona. Bersama Dengan Anggota Ketiga Tim, Multi Nana-Iro, Mereka Bercita-Cita Untuk Mencapai Puncak Liga Beyblade X.

programme.title: Ultraman Orb
programme.desc: Drama Tokusatsu Jepang Yang Menceritakan Kisah Naomi Yumeno Yang Memiliki Mimpi Aneh Tentang Cahaya Raksasa Yang Bersinar Melawan Monster Raksasa. Naomi Yumeno, Jetta Hayami, Dan Shin Matsudo Kemudian Menemukan Binatang Misterius Tak Dikenal Yang Diduga Menyebabkan Aktivitas Meteorologi Yang Aneh. Mereka Menuju Pusat Cuaca Aneh Dan Bertemu Dengan Monster Angin, Maga-Basser! Naomi Dihempas Oleh Angin Ganas Tetapi Diselamatkan Oleh Gelandangan, Gai Kurenai. Dengan Menggunakan Orb Ring-Nya Untuk Membaca Kekuatan Dua Ultra Sebelumnya, Gai Mampu Melakukan Fusion Up Menjadi Prajurit Cahaya Dari Galaksi Yang Jauh, Ultraman Orb!

Program Ini Akan Menampilkan Praktik Sains Dari Kakak Ilmuwan, Pertunjukan Dongeng, Hingga Pertunjukan Bakat Siswa Seperti Menyanyi, Menari, Berolahraga, Dll. Pada Setiap Bagian Program Terdapat Pembelajaran Bagi Siswa Yang Dikemas Lebih Menyenangkan.

Para Smurf Tinggal Di Rumah Berbentuk Jamur Dan Hidup Dengan Damai. Namun, Kedatangan Penyihir Jahat Gargamel Dan Kucingnya, Azrael, Merusak Kedamaian Desa Tersebut. Sehingga Para Smurf Harus Mencari Cara Agar Tidak Ditangkap Oleh Gargamel Dan Azrael.

Pada Musim Ini Jett Memiliki Perubahan Pada Tenaga Supernya Yaitu Menggunakan Mesin Listrik! Memiliki Desain Futuristic Dan Lebih Ramping Dari Sebelumnya, Mereka Dibuat Seperti Itu Agar Sesuai Dengan Konsep Listrik Baru Dan Mereka Juga Menyambut Energi Terbaru Yang Bersih Dan Ramah Lingkungan.

Albert Yang Merupakan Seorang Ilmuwan, Menciptakan Monster Baru Agar Lebih Banyak Kaiju Yang Diciptakannya. Dia Berencana Untuk Mendapatkan Geostone Tersebut, Sehingga Mengirimkan Kaiju Ke Bumi. Khawatir Bahwa Bumi Dalam Bahaya Dari Monster Luar Angkasa Tersebut, V Seorang Polisi Luar Angkasa Melihat Keberanian Scoot Dalam Mempertahankan Desanya Kemudian Memberikan Scoot Sebuah Rise Spark Yang Bisa Merubahnya Menjadi Riseman. Tokek Adalah Anak Yang Lucu Dan Periang, Sedangkan Hoho Adalah Seorang Anak Jakarta Yang Dilahirkan Dari Keluarga Kaya Raya, Sifatnya Manja Dan Tidak Mengerti Sama Sekali Tentang Islam. Tapi Ternyata Dari Ibra Lah Hoho Banyak Mendapatkan Pelajaran Hidup Dan Kisah-Kisah Teladan Nabi Muhammad Shalallahu Alaihi Wassalam.

Cinta Sedalam Rindu?menceritakan Aluna (Esta Pramanita) yang menyembunyikan identitasnya di?game online?sebagai Gulagula. Tak disangka, ia dekat dengan Ezra (Farhan Rasyid) yang memakai nama Ezy. programme.title: Jejak Duka Diandra

Dimitri terjebak dalam situasi sulit akibat ulah sang adik, Jupiter (Bizael) yang menuduh Dimitri melecehkan Yunita. Hubungan Dimitri dengan Diandra pun semakin merenggang. Tuduhan lainnya juga harus diterima Dimitri sebagai penyebab insiden kecelakaan seorang wanita. Posisi Dimitri semakin terpojok setelah Diandra yang diminta sebagai saksi justru tidak berpihak kepadanya hingga Dimitri mendapat sanksi mendekam di balik jeruji besi selama lima tahun.Lima tahun berlalu, Dimitri hidup bebas dan melanjutkan usaha sang ayah. Ia pun membuka kisah cinta baru dengan Melissa (Tasya Panggabean). Takdir pun berkata lain, pertemuan Dimitri dan Diandra kembali terjadi...kisah selengkapnya, silakan saksikan hanya di SCTV.
